<P>
   PARTY-OF-FIVE _ Fox's ``Party of Five'' has its finale tonight.
Never a huge hit, it had a strong cult following and launched the
careers of Neve Campbell and Jennifer Love Hewitt. (Kloer, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 12.
