   ROBERDS-SIDE _ DAYTON _ We talk with employees to get their
reaction and insight into the downfall of Roberds. Also, we get
reax from customers, some of whom have purchases that will be left
in legal limbo. (Bischoff, Dayton Daily News). 15-20.
</P>
