little S2000 sports cars. The day is made for convertibles. I can
hardly wait to put the top down and take to the flower-lined
roadways. Except I can't start the car or figure out how to release
the fuel door. (Sharp, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). Includes
1-column color photograph of columnist.
