player personnel Bobby Grier has a final meeting with Patriots
owner Robert Kraft at Foxboro Stadium, presumably to get a
handshake and perhaps a severance package. By Nick Cafardo.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
