   The lowest restricted and unrestricted round trip airfares.
</P>
<P>
   EVENTS CALENDAR 0507 -- 2 x 5 1/8 -- Weekly travel feature
</P>
<P>
   Locations, dates and contacts for events around the world.
</P>
<P>
   Eds note: WHATSDOING_Singapore and VITAL STATS_Singapore will
move 05-09-00.
</P>
<P>
   BUSINESS
</P>
