</P>
<P>
   BONFIRE-HIGHLIGHTS _ COLLEGE STATION, Texas _ Main findings of
the report, at a glance. (Gamboa, Ward, Austin American-Statesman).
8-10.
</P>
<P>
   BONFIRE-REACT _ AUSTIN _ What do state officials (Lt. Gov. Rick
Perry, former Comptroller John Sharp), former Aggies, other
authorities think? How will their like/dislike of the report play
in what happens next? (Greenberger, Austin American-Statesman). 25.
</P>
<P>
